criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  At least 18 years of age;

          -  Hospitalized patients

          -  Suspected or confirmed infection;

          -  Anticipated IV vancomycin treatment for 24 hours or more.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with renal replacement therapy (peritoneal dialysis, continuous renal
             replacement therapy or hemodialysis);

          -  Treatment of vancomycin in continuous infusion;
